May be an image of text that says 'Every once in a while, my daughter and I will be snuggling, and I will move my arm away to grab my water, or check the time, and she immediately grabs my arm and pulls it back. It's the sweet, subtle reminder that I am her real life security blanket, and I'll take every opportunity can to be that for her. Scary Momny'.
